@startuml SME_Ops_Sequence_Dashboard
title UC19 — View dashboard KPI summary — §2.3.7

actor Manager
participant "Dashboard UI" as Web
participant "DashboardController" as API
participant "DashboardService" as Svc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Manager -> Web : open /dashboard
Web -> API : GET /dashboard/summary
API -> Svc : getSummary(orgId)
Svc -> DB : aggregate Sales (revenue, profit)
Svc -> DB : aggregate OperationalExpense
Svc -> DB : count products, customers, low stock
Svc --> API : KPI DTO (incl. netProfit)
API --> Web : JSON
Web --> Manager : render cards & charts

@enduml
